name: New Balance 999 X CNCPTS US NAVE S.E.A.L
description:
Inspired by the functional rigor behind the high-performance amphibious boot called the OTB Abyss II. It’s designed to excel with high pursuit traction, durability and comfort as created for the US Navy SEALs. The SEAL 999 optimizes some of it’s key features – stain resistant microfiber suede, ballistic mesh and ultra-breathable nylon panels allowing the SEAL 999 to thrive in a host of diverse conditions.

Stain Resistant microfiber suede
Ballistic Mesh
Ultra-breathable nylon panels
Gusseted Tongue
Rubber N on medial side for repelling descents
Morse code encryption branding on the tongue
Military 999 typography
Topographic insole and stitched Concepts patch on footbed
Multiple lace options
